ED_Title: Report of the Economic and Social Council
ED_DecisionText: At its 26th plenary meeting, on 2 November 2021, the General Assembly took note of the report of the Economic and Social Council (footnote: A/76/3).
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of decisions adopted during the main part of the session will be contained in document A/76/49 (Vol. II) after editorial review.
